headline: Has Fair Isaac (FICO) Pulled Too Far Ahead Of Its Cash Flow And Earnings Multiples
summary: If you have been watching Fair Isaac and wondering whether the current share price reflects its true worth, this article will walk through what the numbers are actually saying about value. The stock closed at US$1,581.19, with a 7 day return of a 0.3% decline, a 30 day return of an 11.8% decline, a year to date return of a 3.8% decline, while the 1 year return sits at a 19.7% decline and the 3 year return is a very large gain, alongside a 221.8% gain over 5 years.
